Usage: loadECO [-help] <fileName....> [-suffix <suffix>] [-verbose] [-postMask  | -useGACells <GACoreSiteName>]

-help                                      # Prints out the command usage
<fileName....>                             # Delta file name (string, required)
-postMask                                  # use spare cells (bool, optional)
-suffix <suffix>                           # Name of suffix (string, optional)
-useGACells <GACoreSiteName>               # Name of core site name
                                           # (string, optional)
-verbose                                   # verbose (bool, optional)